graph TD
    U[User] --> Input[User Message/Input]

    Input --> A1[Spanish-Agent]
    Input --> A2[Interaction-Agent]
    Input --> A3[Balance-Agent]
    Input --> A4[Transaction-Agent]

    A1 --> R1[OpenAI API Call - Spanish]
    A2 --> R2[OpenAI API Call - UI Flow]
    A3 --> R3[OpenAI API Call - Balance]
    A4 --> R4[OpenAI API Call - Transaction]

    R1 --> O1[Spanish Response]
    R2 --> O2[UI Response]
    R3 --> O3[Balance Info]
    R4 --> O4[Transaction Status]

    O1 --> Merge[Aggregate Output]
    O2 --> Merge
    O3 --> Merge
    O4 --> Merge

    Merge --> Final[Final Response to User]
